  "description": "Deterministic backprop training-trace engine — v0.6 ships external trace ingestion: bp import pytorch <sidecar.jsonl> produces observer-mode v0.4.0 receipts with attestor + source_framework + Rule 14 engine-recompute differential as the load-bearing trust gate. Rule 15 (skip-basis required) + Rule 16 (gated attestation digest binding) close the laundering attack surface. Foreign PyTorch / JAX traces become evidence sources without becoming trusted authorities — the engine remains the verifier, not a framework wrapper. Layered on v0.5 softmax+CE, v0.4 authoring spine, v0.3 generalized topology + hybrid tolerance + multi-step receipts.",
